<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10692610>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. A) Aphredoderus sayanus, ANSP 12690, lectotype from a fishpond in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, U.S.A. B) JFBM 50405 A. sayanus from Little Creek, a tributary of the Delaware River in Burlington County, New Jersey, U.S.A. Photo credits: A—Amanda L. Labadie (ANSP), B—Tyler Muller." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10692610/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10692629>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Range and sampling locations of Aphredoderus sayanus, A. gibbosus and A. ornatus specimens used in this study. Sampling locations with black outlines indicate genetic sampling. Type localities from A. sayanus georeferenced to the River Wards section of Philadelphia, PA (pers. comm. Mark Sabaj-Perez, pers. comm. Feb 8, 2022), A. gibbosus to the center of Lake Pontchartrain, LA." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10692629/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

